`,cleanCss=`/* ============================================
   CLEAN TEMPLATE
   ============================================

   Overall feel:
     Warm, approachable, and polished. Soft neutral
     tones with an amber accent give a friendly but
     professional impression.

   Typography:
     Outfit (sans-serif) at 10.5pt with 1.65 line-height.
     Name is semi-bold at 24pt with tight tracking.
     Title is regular weight in the warm accent colour.

   Header:
     Fully centred. A hairline rule (1px, very light
     grey) below the header block separates it from
     the body without being heavy.

   Sections (h2):
     Small (8pt) all-caps labels in the accent colour
     with wide tracking. A 1px bottom border in
     near-white grey provides a subtle underline.

   Summary paragraph:
     Centred at 88% max-width, in muted grey —
     reads like a tagline beneath the name block.

   Job titles (h4):
     Light grey (#9ca3af), no weight — purely
     supplementary to h3 role/company text.

   Inline emphasis (em):
     Rendered without italic in light grey, suitable
     for date ranges and location annotations.

   Lists:
     Outlined circle bullets (border only, no fill)
     in the accent colour — distinct and refined.

   Palette:
     Near-black (#111827) headings, neutral grey
     (#4b5563) body text on white. Theme colour
     defaults to amber (#d97706).

   Scoped under .template-clean
   ============================================ */

